{"tid":2070680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★旺角「一樓一」鳳姐遇劫　警調查兩日　拘28歲男子","createTime":"2020-06-19T09:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T10:25:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5b40ec2024f3f9eb91a2092c9251949d0fd99b58","tid":2070680,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:32:46.000Z","msg":"旺角鳳姐周三（6月17日）遭嫖客持刀劫走逾500元．旺角警區刑事調查隊人員接手調查案件，經調查後，今日（19日）凌晨在深水埗區拘捕28歲姓鄧男子，涉嫌行劫，他現正被扣留調查。警方人員同時在疑犯身上起回涉案摺刀。<br />\n<br />\n周三下午3時51分，警方接獲1名46歲姓周女子報案，指她於旺角太子道西135號一單位被1名男子懷疑以一把約16厘米長的摺刀指嚇，並劫去約540元現金。現場消息指，案發於唐3樓「1樓1鳳」單位，1名操鄉音鳳姐接待完1名男子後，他不但未付款，更向鳳姐亮刀，劫財後逃去無蹤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/488137/%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E4%B8%80%E6%A8%93%E4%B8%80-%E9%B3%B3%E5%A7%90%E9%81%87%E5%8A%AB-%E8%AD%A6%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%85%A9%E6%97%A5-%E6%8B%9828%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F488137%2F%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A8%2593%25E4%25B8%2580-%25E9%25B3%25B3%25E5%25A7%2590%25E9%2581%2587%25E5%258A%25AB-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E6%258B%259828%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84Cwy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=b0161ef8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/488137/%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92-%E4%B8%80%E6%A8%93%E4%B8%80-%E9%B3%B3%E5%A7%90%E9%81%87%E5%8A%AB-%E8%AD%A6%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E5%85%A9%E6%97%A5-%E6%8B%9828%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90</a>"},{"pid":"e93bb6aad0b1a6c6c6ff1103da4af9b9af4b1b38","tid":2070680,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\